of the division

127
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:40,890
there will be no struggle
within the family.

128
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:47,090
Forget about finding
a city in that region.

129
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:49,030
There is not even
a hut there, Panchali.

130
00:11:49,990 --> 00:11:51,090
How will you live there?

131
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:58,960
I am certain you know
how to make a hut, My Lord.

132
00:12:00,090 --> 00:12:02,090
That would be more than
sufficient for me.

133
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:11,000
Panchali is correct,
Nakul.

134
00:12:14,090 --> 00:12:17,090
Creating something from scratch
is always more gratifying.

135
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:22,060
And brother Dhritarashtra
will give

136
00:12:22,820 --> 00:12:23,920
that region to you quite easily.

137
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:26,990
But living there

138
00:12:28,050 --> 00:12:30,000
will be exceedingly
difficult, Draupadi.

139
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,600
But living there

140
00:13:02,730 --> 00:13:04,760
will be exceedingly
troublesome, dear.

141
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:10,790
Troubles?

142
00:13:18,660 --> 00:13:21,660
Difficulties give birth to glory

143
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:26,830
fame and prestige.

144
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,600
It is the mother to all three.

145
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:36,800
We shall ask for that region.

146
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:38,590
I have no region with me
which I can give to them

147
00:13:38,660 --> 00:13:39,800
and yet preserve
the prosperity of Hastinapur.

148
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:44,660
If I have to protect my kingdom

149
00:13:44,830 --> 00:13:47,530
then I shall require
prosperity, uncle.

150
00:13:47,590 --> 00:13:48,760
