151
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:58,770
I assure you,
Dhritarashtra

152
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:01,800
that Hastinapur shall be

153
00:14:02,730 --> 00:14:04,800
protected by Yudhishthir and me.

154
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:08,600
Whenever you need us

155
00:14:09,690 --> 00:14:12,670
Yudhishthir and I
shall come to your aid.

156
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:14,530
And Yudhishthir

157
00:14:14,690 --> 00:14:17,670
will never attack Hastinapur.

158
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:22,640
I believe that,
uncle.

159
00:14:26,730 --> 00:14:29,710
But unfortunately, if such a
situation arises in the future

160
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:32,570
or my son does
something unrighteous

161
00:14:34,490 --> 00:14:36,730
then you shall certainly
attack Hastinapur, uncle.

162
