to a battle.

173
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:39,540
He will certainly slay me
in the battle, uncle.

174
00:15:41,660 --> 00:15:43,640
He too is like my son.

175
00:15:47,690 --> 00:15:50,500
I shall place my head on his lap

176
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:53,430
and bid adieu to this life.

177
00:15:54,690 --> 00:15:58,400
Then I shall certainly
go to heaven, uncle.

178
00:16:00,430 --> 00:16:01,430
I shall

179
