The number of sacrifices he has
made for the Kuru kingdom

189
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:51,600
cannot be achieved by a person

190
00:16:52,460 --> 00:16:54,370
in a single lifetime.

191
00:17:06,390 --> 00:17:08,390
