kingdom his entire life, uncle.

202
00:19:11,060 --> 00:19:12,130
Now, we five brothers

203
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:15,110
and our wife will be
at his service forever.

204
00:19:30,230 --> 00:19:31,300
I have firm faith

205
00:19:32,260 --> 00:19:34,000
that henceforth

206
00:19:34,060 --> 00:19:36,240
grandsire will have to make
no more sacrifices, uncle.

207
00:19:38,030 --> 00:19:41,100
Promise me, uncle.

208
00:19:43,260 --> 00:19:45,040
Promise me.

209
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:09,200
